"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-golf-1929742-rory-mcilroy-paris-olympics-ireland-gb-golf\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Rory McIlroyis setting his sights on gold at the2024 Paris Olympics- but he will not be seeking success in the name of Great Britain.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Gilmore\", \"score\": 0.9995748011776934, \"rank\": 0.0004253796696078134, \"text\": \"Rory\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Gilmore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Gilmore\"}, {\"begin\": 121, \"end\": 134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999440661, \"rank\": 4.507282123117267e-11, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And after a disappointing display atThe Openin July, thegolflegend is as hungry as ever to bring honour to Irish shores.\", \"from\": 136, \"to\": 256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 243, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9943145785634739, \"rank\": 0.003819980465906323, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years after narrowly missing out on a medal at Tokyo 2020, the Holywood-born golfer is returning to the Summer Games with hopes of glorious gold.\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's tournament runs from Thursday and culminates in Sunday's finale when the three medal-winners will be announced in the French capital.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9852522048431347, \"rank\": 0.005856542979627555, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Northern Irishman McIlroy will be competing on Ireland's behalf, just as he did during his Olympic debut in Japan three years prior.\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 611, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9992689156239777, \"rank\": 0.000563052648062579, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8570863037163535, \"rank\": 0.16180391769117314, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite being eligible to represent either Ireland or Team GB at the Summer Games, the decision has always been straightforward for the four-time major winner, reportsThe Mirror.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9992689156239777, \"rank\": 0.000563052648062579, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6555032549372396, \"rank\": 0.5255454358705065, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIlroy, 35, has never wavered in his allegiance despite having the unique privilege of choosing between two teams.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like in Tokyo, the golf icon is eager to bring glory to the Emerald Isle this weekend.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6028326978668788, \"rank\": 0.6588348802422263, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Once I left trying not to upset anyone aside, then it was actually a pretty easy decision,\\\" he said ahead of Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6028326978668788, \"rank\": 0.6588348802422263, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The decision was I am going to play golf for the country or the nation that I have always played for through my junior and amateur days and now into the professional game.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's Ireland.\\\"\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1392, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9992689156239777, \"rank\": 0.000563052648062579, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the political divide, when it comes to the Olympics, athletes from both Northern Ireland and the Republic of Ireland unite under a single banner.\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9753501559485961, \"rank\": 0.025272814999466497, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIlroy found himself in a complex situation due to his background but has always represented Ireland in golf.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9992689156239777, \"rank\": 0.000563052648062579, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I made it more difficult for myself than I needed to,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the Olympics offering a choice, for McIlroy there was none, as his lifelong allegiance to playing for Ireland has never been up for debate, as he sees it.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1847, \"end\": 1854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9992689156239777, \"rank\": 0.000563052648062579, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"Even though the Olympics has given me this choice, there really wasn't a choice because all I have done throughout my life is play golf for Ireland so why would that change just because the tournament has changed.\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 2129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2056, \"end\": 2063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9992689156239777, \"rank\": 0.000563052648062579, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was my decision.\\\"\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McIlroy missed his initial chance to compete at Rio 2016 after withdrawing due to fears over the Zika virus.\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2262, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But he's since said he later regretted that decision before seizing his opportunity in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2350, \"end\": 2355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6028326978668788, \"rank\": 0.6588348802422263, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2416, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2481, \"end\": 2486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999681677, \"rank\": 3.175678666657839e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2562, \"end\": 2574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9960168333026775, \"rank\": 0.0039990952265231555, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  He came tantalisingly close to medalling and said afterwards: \\\"I'd never tried to finish third so hard in my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 3008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But alas, he still finished just off the podium after losing out in a bronze medal play-off.\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As McIlroy chases an elusive win 10 years on from securing his last major title, Olympic glory could offer some solace.\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And in some ways, snatching the title from American Xander Schauffele could be an even more special feat considering such a chance arises only once every four years.\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3266, \"end\": 3274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999150777548, \"rank\": 3.3276062656511176e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3275, \"end\": 3292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xander Schauffele\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3527, \"end\": 3540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.567695130367835e-22, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3576, \"end\": 3589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.567695130367835e-22, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"